{"tid":1728001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（習思廣益）林斯疑似精神有問題，佢任內定立嘅惡法可廢？","createTime":"2019-11-16T16:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T16:26:45.000Z","uid":1673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8436a2f6f41fde70f1825ff8d20588573ee0d980","tid":1728001,"uid":1673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:26:45.000Z","msg":"精神病人在法理上不是&mdash;個有能力(capable person)去執行，處理法律事務的人，換句話說，由她推出來的反蒙面法是無效的，因為訂立的人是精神有問題的，條例成為於不能合理情況下定立，法理上該法例不合法地成立，己廢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而林鄭精神狀態異常，政府已經不能運作，依家黑警當道，會唔會係黑警挾持政府？我冇屈9佢㗎！各位巴絲睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2358172604310236&amp;id=100003525586000&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2358172604310236%26id%3D100003525586000%26_rdr&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=96b866b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2358172604310236&amp;id=100003525586000&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇法律巴打比下意見，用呢個point幫唔幫到大家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}